fem.components

Class Triangle

  • java.lang.Object
    • util.model.NamedObject
      • fem.components.AbstractElement
        • fem.components.Triangle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IElement, java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable, INamedObject, IStreamable

    public class Triangle
extends AbstractElement
    This class is abstract with super class AbstractElement. This element is an triangular finite element which contains three nodes.
    Author:
    Darren
